    Log To Console  ........................................
    Log To Console  vSphere version: ${vc_version}
    Log To Console  ESX build: ${esx_build}
    Log To Console  VCSA build: ${vc_build}
    Log To Console  Operating System: ${os}
    Run Keyword If  ${is_skipped}  Log To Console  Skipped...
